// ReportsService — scheduled email-report CRUD + preview +
// send-now + run history.
//
// A ScheduledReport is a persistent blueprint: cron expression,
// timezone, recipients, analytics filter preset, and a template
// variant ('summary' | 'detailed'). The Phase-3.5 dispatcher
